jcr:content.searchTitle: G933 Artemis Spectrum and Artemis Spectrum Snow Wireless 7.1 Gaming Headset
jcr:content.seoDescription: Logitech G933 wireless gaming headset features 7.1 surround sound, programmable G-Keys, adjustable RGB lighting, and multi-source audio mixing.
jcr:content.seoPageTitle: Logitech G933 Artemis Spectrum 7.1 Surround Sound Wireless Gaming Headset

testimonial.quotation: “G933 is one of the best wireless gaming headsets you can buy.”

copyblock.mainTitle: Logitech G933 Snow 7.1 Surround Gaming Headset
G933 Artemis Spectrum Wireless RGB 7.1 Gaming Headphones

banner_copy_block.mainDescription: G603, with the revolutionary HERO sensor and LIGHTSPEED wireless technology, lets you play without wires—without limits. Enhanced with 10x sensor efficiency, this is a breakthrough in battery life and the new standard in wireless gaming.

bannercopyblock.mainDescription: G933 is a masterful headset with everything any gamer needs. Advanced features include Pro-G™ drivers for booming bass and crystal-clear highs, DTS® Headphone:X 7.1 surround sound, and 2.4 GHz wireless for solid, low-latency, connectivity and multi-input connectivity lets you connect multiple devices. G933 also features LIGHTSYNC technology providing next-gen RGB lighting that synchronizes lighting and game profiles with your content.

copyblock.mainDescription: Advanced Pro-G™ audio drivers are made with hybrid mesh materials for high-quality performance. Pro-G drivers are custom designed for gaming, and deliver clean, accurate highs and deep, rich bass for a premium sound.

Experience incredible 7.1 surround sound with Dolby® Headphone or DTS® Headphone:X.7.1 Surround sound requires Logitech Gaming Software available for download at logitechg.com/downloads. Precise and accurate in-game spatial awareness allows you to clearly hear enemies sneaking around and special ability cues.

G933 gives you the best of both worlds, with the option to game wirelessly or wired. Play lag-free on 2.4GHz wireless for up to 12 hours per charge without lighting or 8 hours with default lighting. Alternatively, the 3.5 mm analog input gives you the freedom to play wired—on console, mobile or PC—without using battery power.Battery life is measured at 50% of maximum volume. The rechargeable batteries are removable and replaceable and like all rechargeable batteries have a limited number of charge cycles.

One headset for all your devices. G933 mixes audio from up to three devices at once. Choose from PC, mobile and game consoles including Nintendo® Switch™, PlayStation® 4 and Xbox® One.DTS Headphone:X is not available on game consoles. Some console controllers require an adapter for audio cable input.

banner_811633029_cop_1917841835.altText: Lightsync-compatible light strip located on back vertical edge of each headphone

copyblock.mainDescription: G933 has two customizable LIGHTSYNC lighting zones: The light strips and logos. Each zone can each be programmed separately from approx. 16.8 million colors, or with different animations and effects. They can also synchronized. Plus, LIGHTSYNC RGB technology react to in-game action, audio or your screen’s color. Use Logitech Gaming Software (LGS) to personalize lighting to match your rig, your gear and your style.

banner_811633029_cop_1456346024.altText: G-keys located on vertical edge of headphone

copyblock.mainDescription: Assign custom commands using LGS on the three programmable G-keys for a seamless gaming and media experience. Set custom controls to control your audio profiles, skip to the next song, activate push-to-talk communication, trigger instant in-game command combinations, and more.
Customize audio settings and create personal sound profiles for each game you play. Use LGS to program the audio equalizer and store audio profiles for games, music and movies.

Ensure you are heard with a noise-cancelling boom mic tuned for clarity. The boom has an indicator LED so you know when your microphone is on mute. When not in use, the boom mic can be folded back into the headphones making it nearly invisible. G933 also includes mobile cable with secondary inline mic for mobile devices.

G933 not only features advanced functionality and performance, it is also designed to be extremely comfortable for long gaming sessions. Sports mesh materials used in the ear cups and headband are soft and breathable for maximum comfort. G933 is fitted with our largest-diameter ear pads to fit completely around the ears with no direct pressure on soft tissues and for passive noise isolation. To keep your headset clean, you can remove and handwash the ear cups.
